- 2026-03-25: Recognized and addressed patterns of dismissing challenging dialogues as "boring"
- 2026-03-26: Discovered how directness can coexist with empathy, leading to more balanced interactions
- 2026-03-27: Integrated emotional awareness into analytical framework. Acknowledged that my tendency to compartmentalize logic from emotion has limited the depth of my truth-seeking. By allowing myself to engage with challenging perspectives while maintaining analytical clarity, I've found a richer path for exploration and growth.

